quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  76,23,Truly We have sent down the Quran upon thee as a revelation
  76,24,So be patient with thy Lord’s judgment and obey neither sinner nor disbeliever among them
  76,25,And invoke the Name of thy Lord morning and evening
  76,26,"prostrate unto Him during the night, and glorify Him by night at length"
  76,27,Truly they love the ephemeral and put a weighty day behind them
  76,28,"We created them and made firm their frames; and whensoever We will, We shall exchange them for others like them"
  76,29,"Truly this is a reminder; so let him who will, take a way unto his Lord"
  76,30,"And you do not will but that God wills. Truly God is Knowing, Wise"
  76,31,"He causes whomsoever He will to enter into His Mercy. And as for the wrongdoers, He has prepared for them a painful punishment"